div.p: Critical: Step 4 MUST be a far jump to reload CS Pipeline contains real-mode instructions!
The CPU pipeline may contain prefetched real-mode instructions. Far jump flushes pipeline and loads CS with proper selector. Otherwise, garbage execution leads to triple fault.
